00:47:37.250 --> 00:47:40.850
So the Mach-Zehnder,
I mentioned that this

00:47:40.850 --> 00:47:43.640
is like a transmission
interferometer.

00:47:43.640 --> 00:47:50.180
The Michelson is like a
reflection interferometer.

00:47:50.180 --> 00:47:52.400
Both of these sorts
of interferometers

00:47:52.400 --> 00:47:55.430
are used in
microscopy, actually.

00:47:55.430 --> 00:47:58.880
And so you can make an
interference microscope

00:47:58.880 --> 00:48:01.330
based on this technique.

00:48:01.330 --> 00:48:04.220
And you could put
in here, let's say,

00:48:04.220 --> 00:48:08.540
