of tissue or something on it.

00:48:08.540 --> 00:48:11.480
And you could use this to
measure the obstacle path

00:48:11.480 --> 00:48:14.210
in going through that object.

00:48:14.210 --> 00:48:17.320
It's not trivial to do that.

00:48:17.320 --> 00:48:20.570
