01:12:34.110 --> 01:12:37.350
the concept of a
transparency that

01:12:37.350 --> 01:12:44.310
can change the magnitude
and phase of a wave

01:12:44.310 --> 01:12:46.560
by transmitting through it.

01:12:46.560 --> 01:12:53.410
And so this shows
