01:14:19.300 --> 01:14:23.390
So this transparency can
change the attenuation.

01:14:23.390 --> 01:14:26.720
So the black bits are
going to absorb the light.

01:14:26.720 --> 01:14:29.600
But it could also
change the phase.

01:14:29.600 --> 01:14:31.400
So phase delay.

01:14:31.400 --> 01:14:34.160
And both of these
are going to be--

01:14:34.160 --> 01:14:37.610
both of these effects are going
