01:14:41.930 --> 01:14:43.310
its thickness.

01:14:43.310 --> 01:14:48.540
And as it points out
here, in some cases,

01:14:48.540 --> 01:14:51.620
you might be able to think
of these quantities--

01:14:51.620 --> 01:14:54.590
the attenuation and
the phase delay--

