I'm not even sure--

01:33:45.212 --> 01:33:48.110
I always think of
the Poisson spot

01:33:48.110 --> 01:33:51.770
as being what you get
from an opaque object,

01:33:51.770 --> 01:33:54.980
rather than for--

01:33:54.980 --> 01:33:57.512
but maybe that's the Arago spot.

01:33:57.512 --> 01:33:58.970
GEORGE BARBASTATHIS:
